name: $10 surprise ~ in your size!
description:
Once a year in JULY we have our annual $10 bin sale at Shipwreck day in Anacortes, Wa. 

 These $10 t-shirts are leftovers from the end of editions from when we change design colors, or brands we no longer use, or sometimes just the last few remaining in a design that we're not reprinting. Sometimes we find a tiny hole by the tag, or the print is slightly off center, but there's nothing truly wrong with them, they're just special. 

 Many of you who live far away have said that you wish you could attend too, so we've decided to make the offer on our web site as well until they're all sold out!

Use the scroll down menu to choose your size in either Guys (unisex) or Ladies and we'll pick a random shirt for you in your chosen size.

Sorry no returns on these t-shirts, and no picking your design. These are totally GRAB BAG style, so it's a surprise!
